value.text: Use P2596 (culture) as a main value instead of qualifying P31/P279 statements in an attempt to link a cuisine to a culture or region.
Use P2341 (indigenous to) as a main value instead of qualifying P31/P279 statements in an attempt to link a culture to a region.
For main values consider using P131 (in administrative unit), P1269 (facet of), etc.

The English word "of" has many different meanings and other languages like Chinese often don't have words that directly correspond to the English meaning. In most cases it's desirable to use more specific properties than this. For alternative properties, see [[Wikidata:WikiProject Data Quality/Issues/P642]]
